---
title: Italian-Spiced Chicken with Tomato Rice and Roasted Green Beans
description: Italian seasoning and blackening spice gives this pan-seared chicken a major flavor kick. Tangy tomato rice and roasted green beans completes this simple yet tasty dinner.
